prompt: a luxurious ball gown wedding dress with shimmering crystal embellishments throughout. The gown features a semi-sheer illusion neckline, elegant puff sleeves in three-quarter length, and a fitted bodice that flows into a dramatic full ball gown skirt. The entire dress is adorned with intricate beading and sequins creating a sparkle effect. The dress is made of premium tulle and organza with a crystallized overlay that catches the light. A delicate crystal tiara complements the regal silhouette. The dress has a classic Victorian-inspired design with modern glamour, photographed against classical architectural elements.
